      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it shows in every single detail. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the actual new-car price tag, this is the one for you! Come take it for a spin, I promise you're going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
