    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom-ready condition since the day it left the dealership. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings, having been professionally ceramic coated and strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover. Inside, the cabin remains impeccable; the premium leather seats are supple and free of any creasing or bolster wear, and it still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every button, switch, and electronic component functions perfectly, reflecting its pampered life. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. It has never seen rain or snow, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a definitive example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
